README llvm

PRECAUTION

    Note, that updating major versions of llvm (in x.y.z changing x or
    y) requires rebuilding packages like xorg-server, mesa, glu as
    they depend on this package.  Have revdep(1) point out potential
    candidates for rebuilds after the llvm update.


